  ],
  "description": "Two Sine oscillators — fundamental and seventh partial (+7 semitones, tuned to the 7-limit harmonic) — drift through a 7-limit attractor field. Journey mode engaged: the field slowly evolves over time, pulling intervals through the 7-limit just network. Reverb opens the space. The septimal minor seventh (7:4) is the destination the field is always seeking.",
